<h2 id="hobbies">Hobbies</h2>

<p>Dr. Kahveci is a <a href="https://twitter.com/iMuratKahveci/status/660367394221768704">runner</a> and <a href="https://twitter.com/iMuratKahveci/status/1267517868167626752/photo/1">road-biker</a>. Since Jan 2019, he has been doing <a href="https://twitter.com/iMuratKahveci/status/1105646512334344192">strength training</a>. He has been playing <a href="https://lichess.org/@/iMuratK">chess</a> since his childhood.</p>

<h3 id="biking-activities">Biking Activities</h3>

<p>Relying on several live tracking software such as <a href="https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiL4LnZoJvqAhVBJ80KHTzxAvsQFjAAegQIDhAC&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.runtastic.com%2F&amp;usg=AOvVaw3wAwVH-eMwu1G_pCsk6SlB">Adidas Runtastic</a>, <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/activity/id1208224953">watchOS Activity</a>, and <a href="https://www.strava.com/">Strava</a>, Dr. Kahveci keeps the logs of his biking activities and regularly posts them to Biking Activities.</p>

